---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Topeka, KS Auto Repair | Total Turf & Auto"
  description="Total Turf & Auto on NW Topeka Blvd offers honest auto repair and maintenance for Topeka, KS drivers. Local shop, straight answers, fair pricing."
>
  <!-- ===== Page hero ===== -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a> / <span>Topeka, KS</span></p>
      <h1>Auto Repair in Topeka, KS</h1>
      <p>A locally owned shop on NW Topeka Blvd, serving drivers across Shawnee County with honest work and straight answers.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Intro ===== -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split">
        <div class="split-body reveal">
          <span class="eyebrow">Our Location</span>
          <h2>A North Topeka Shop, Built for Local Drivers</h2>
          <p class="lead">Total Turf &amp; Auto is a full-service auto repair shop at 2700 NW Topeka Blvd, sitting on the north side of Topeka just across the Kansas River from downtown.</p>
          <p>We work on cars, trucks, and SUVs for drivers all over Shawnee County, from quick oil changes to bigger diagnostic and engine work. Our location keeps us close to the heart of the city. Highway 24 runs right past us, US-75 is a few minutes away, and downtown Topeka is a short drive across the river.</p>
          <p>That makes drop-offs simple whether you live in North Topeka, work downtown, or commute in from one of the smaller towns nearby. We focus on doing the job right and telling you straight what your vehicle needs. No upsells you did not ask for, no guesswork on the bill.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="split-media reveal">
          <img src="/assets/img/work/shop-interior.webp" alt="Inside the Total Turf & Auto shop in north Topeka, KS" width="600" height="700" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Neighborhoods & zip codes ===== -->
  <section class="section section--soft">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Topeka Neighborhoods</span>
        <h2>The Areas We Serve</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="split">
        <div class="split-body reveal">
          <h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:10px;">Neighborhoods</h3>
          <p>We see customers from across the Topeka area, including folks in the NOTO Arts District and Oakland just down the road, longtime residents around Potwin Place and College Hill, families in Westboro and Country Club, drivers from Highland Park and Holliday Park on the south side, and commuters coming in from Croco and the east side. If you live in town, we are an easy stop.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="split-body reveal">
          <h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:10px;">Zip Codes</h3>
          <p>Our shop sits in 66617, and we regularly serve the surrounding North Topeka zips of 66608 and 66618. Downtown and central Topeka customers in 66603, 66606, 66607, and 66612 are a quick drive over the river, and we see plenty of west and south side drivers from 66604, 66610, 66611, and 66614 as well.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Surrounding communities ===== -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Beyond Topeka</span>
        <h2>Serving the Surrounding Communities</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="owner-card reveal">
        <p>Plenty of our customers drive in from the smaller communities around Shawnee and Jackson counties. To the west we see folks from Silver Lake and Rossville. North brings drivers from Hoyt, Mayetta, and Meriden. East of town we serve Tecumseh and Perry, and Auburn and Berryton drivers come up from the south. If you are within a short drive of Topeka, we are worth the trip.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Why Topeka drivers choose us ===== -->
  <section class="section section--soft">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Why Local Drivers Choose Us</span>
        <h2>A Topeka Shop You Can Actually Trust</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card reveal">
          <div class="why-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 3l7 4v5c0 5-3.5 8-7 9-3.5-1-7-4-7-9V7z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Straightforward Estimates</h3>
          <p>The work is explained in plain language before we start, with prices you can plan around.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card reveal">
          <div class="why-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Local Accountability</h3>
          <p>A locally owned shop, not a national chain reading from a script.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card reveal">
          <div class="why-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14.7 6.3a4 4 0 00-5.4 5.4L3 18l3 3 6.3-6.3a4 4 0 005.4-5.4l-2.8 2.8-2.6-.7-.7-2.6z"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Real Experience</h3>
          <p>Hands-on work from routine maintenance to diagnostics and larger repairs on cars, trucks, and diesels.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card reveal">
          <div class="why-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0118 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Easy to Reach</h3>
          <p>Convenient north Topeka location with quick access from US-75, Highway 24, and downtown.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Local context ===== -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Local Driving Conditions</span>
        <h2>Why Maintenance Matters More in Topeka</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="owner-card reveal">
        <p>Topeka is hard on vehicles. Summers run hot and humid, winters bring ice storms and stretches well below freezing, and the freeze-thaw cycle chews up roads and suspensions. Road salt during the winter takes a toll on brake lines, undercarriages, and electrical connections. Add in the highway miles a lot of locals put on I-70, I-470, and US-75, plus the gravel and rural routes outside the city limits, and routine maintenance matters more here than people realize. Staying on top of fluids, brakes, tires, and cooling systems is the difference between a long-lasting vehicle and an expensive surprise.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CTA ===== -->
  <section class="section section--soft">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-banner reveal">
        <div>
          <h2>Schedule Your Topeka Auto Repair</h2>
          <p>Give us a call at (785) 925-4040 or stop by 2700 NW Topeka Blvd. We will take a look, talk through your options, and get you back on the road.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-banner-actions">
          <a href="tel:+17859254040" class="btn btn--white btn--lg">(785) 925-4040</a>
          <a href="/contact#book" class="btn btn--lime btn--lg">Request Appointment</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
